      "theme": "brightness, temperature, and speed",
      "intro": "Kapampangan adjectives often begin with 'ma-', a prefix meaning 'having the quality of'. In this lesson you will learn four adjectives: 'maliwanag' (bright/clear), 'mainit' (hot/warm), 'malambat' (slow), and 'maliksi' (fast/agile). Notice that 'malambat' and 'maliksi' are antonyms.",
